FILE: A crime scene cordoned off. Flickr.com/Adam Gerard DURBAN - eThekwini Mayor Mxolisi Kaunda has condemned the murder of a senior municipal official. The 36-year-old woman was shot several times at a water depot in Ottawa, north of Durban. The depot fills tankers to supply areas affected by the floods. READ: eThekwini municipal official gunned down The motive for the murder is not immediately known. Kaunda has urged anyone with information to contact the police.